463
00:28:23.514 --> 00:28:24.648
Ah.

464
00:28:24.783 --> 00:28:25.784
Tolkien altså.

465
00:28:25.916 --> 00:28:26.984
Kapitel 48.

466
00:28:27.117 --> 00:28:30.687
Jeg flytter, at vi
bestiller endnu en runde først.

467
00:28:30.822 --> 00:28:33.123
Et mirakel. Min bror køber.

468
00:28:33.257 --> 00:28:34.759
Varna.

469
00:28:34.893 --> 00:28:38.028
- Mine herrer, det samme igen? 
